  "name": "Compressed Moissanite X-Grade",
  "description": "This variant of Moissanite ore is especially prized by Gallente engineers for use in large-scale construction projects. Deposits have been held in reserve until such a time as the Federation needed them.\n\nUnlike regular Moissanite ore, X-Grade is more stable and can be reprocessed without specialized equipment into <a href=showinfo:34>Tritanium</a> and <a href=showinfo:35>Pyerite</a>, as well as providing <a href=showinfo:92571>Crystalline Moissanite</a>, which is valuable to the Gallente Federation.\n\nThis material is compressed and a much more compact form of the original material.",
